181
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:05,320
The masters are here.

182
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:07,630
Smile, every one of you.

183
00:11:08,150 --> 00:11:09,550
Smile.

184
00:11:09,870 --> 00:11:11,670
Smile!

185
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:21,150
Greetings, Master Huo.

186
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:23,750
This is...

187
00:11:24,270 --> 00:11:26,600
This is the director of Renxin Orphanage.

188
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:28,630
Everyone knows

189
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:32,030
