for over 20 years.

190
00:11:32,030 --> 00:11:33,320
Renxin Orphanage

191
00:11:33,670 --> 00:11:35,150
is the fruit of our labor.

192
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:39,390
Nanny Sun has been dedicated
to taking care

193
00:11:39,390 --> 00:11:40,870
of these children for over 20 years.

194
00:11:40,870 --> 00:11:42,200
She has done her utmost,

195
00:11:42,550 --> 00:11:44,810
