196
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:47,840
I've long heard

197
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:49,870
Master Huo is a man of great love.

198
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:52,630
This is truly a great virtue.

199
00:11:52,870 --> 00:11:54,440
I'm flattered.

200
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:57,750
I just want to repay
the kindness Master Huo gave

201
00:11:57,750 --> 00:12:00,390
over 20 years ago.

202
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:04,390
I'm doing it willingly
for the sake of the children.

203
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:06,360
It's nothing worth mentioning.

204
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:08,160
It's nothing worth mentioning.

205
00:12:09,150 --> 00:12:10,910
What a group of good kids.

206
00:12:11,670 --> 00:12:13,360
You've taught them well.

207
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:15,970
They are so quiet and sensible.

208
00:12:17,750 --> 00:12:20,750
Today is the opening day
of Qingyu's aviation school.

209
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,200
Grandfather specially brought the children

210
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,790
