in the military for generations,

220
00:12:39,670 --> 00:12:41,130
so we have killed too much.

221
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:43,130
Today is a good opportunity

222
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:45,360
to raise funds for the children.

223
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:46,080
Good.

224
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:47,120
Very good.

225
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:57,820
They call it a fundraiser,

226
00:12:58,200 --> 00:12:59,670
