all go into their pockets in the end?

227
00:12:59,670 --> 00:13:00,390
Come on.

228
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:03,870
-Turn right.
-The Huo family suffered this time.

229
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:06,100
This little donation is nothing.

230
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,360
Let's go, Mother.

231
00:13:08,670 --> 00:13:09,600
Wait.

232
