Wait.

233
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:15,320
Turn right, be good.

234
00:13:18,150 --> 00:13:19,720
Don't fall.

235
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:27,910
Don't fall.

236
00:13:33,670 --> 00:13:34,670
Nanny Sun.

237
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:43,550
Miss Fang.

238
00:13:44,150 --> 00:13:45,630
What brings you here?

239
00:13:46,630 --> 00:13:48,670
The children are going to perform soon.

240
00:13:48,670 --> 00:13:49,800
I came to take a look.

241
00:14:05,790 --> 00:14:07,440
Don't get your hands dirty.

242
00:14:17,870 --> 00:14:20,070
You really taught them well, Nanny Sun.

243
00:14:20,870 --> 00:14:22,150
These young children

244
00:14:23,150 --> 00:14:25,080
