indeed.

249
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:35,750
Don't you find these children pitiful?

250
00:14:36,910 --> 00:14:39,630
They are either sick or disabled,

251
00:14:39,910 --> 00:14:41,440
and none of them have a home.

252
00:14:42,150 --> 00:14:44,550
If it weren't for Master Huo's kindness

253
00:14:44,550 --> 00:14:46,030
