256
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:51,240
or starve to death on the streets?

257
00:14:51,750 --> 00:14:53,200
Am I right?

258
00:14:57,270 --> 00:14:59,600
For these children
to be where they are today,

259
00:14:59,600 --> 00:15:01,390
Nanny Sun and Master Huo

260
00:15:01,910 --> 00:15:03,440
really went to great lengths.

261
00:15:03,440 --> 00:15:04,700
I wouldn't dare say so.

262
00:15:05,030 --> 00:15:07,750
We need people like Miss Fang

263
00:15:07,750 --> 00:15:09,440
