267
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:18,200
Thank you for the reminder, Miss Fang.

268
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:22,320
I'll go now.

269
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:27,150
I'll...

270
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:28,600
