with the Huo family.

569
00:33:46,200 --> 00:33:46,920
Susu.

570
00:33:49,880 --> 00:33:51,200
A family friend, the Huo family,

571
00:33:51,200 --> 00:33:53,060
is holding a banquet in Beicheng.

572
00:33:53,400 --> 00:33:55,600
Qingyu asked me to attend on his behalf.

573
00:33:55,640 --> 00:33:56,640
Come with me.

574
00:34:01,070 --> 00:34:02,310
For Lan,

575
00:34:03,160 --> 00:34:05,290
I had to use you to enter the Huo family.

576
00:34:06,240 --> 00:34:08,150
This might be my only chance.

577
00:34:14,840 --> 00:34:16,300
Go ahead and do your thing.

578
00:34:16,400 --> 00:34:18,070
I want to go take a walk in the garden.

579
00:34:18,070 --> 00:34:18,870
I'll go first.

580
00:34:21,480 --> 00:34:22,880
After sending you away,

581
00:34:23,480 --> 00:34:25,360
I started to carry out my plan.

582
00:34:26,550 --> 00:34:28,320
That was the first time
since I came to Beicheng

583
00:34:28,320 --> 00:34:30,110
that I was so close to Lan—

584
00:34:31,550 --> 00:34:33,030
and also the last.

585
00:35:32,190 --> 00:35:33,230
Lan.

